Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.93,0:08:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,O G550 está a 8.000 quilômetros dos pelotões de Gardes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.01,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Merda.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Obedeça meus comandos!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare, Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.16,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Merda! Vou acertar Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.92,0:09:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.01,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.18,0:10:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi, escuta nós! Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinatose, dano pesado!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Piloto ferido!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana[T0]!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana![T0]!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana[T0]!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.89,0:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuide de Izana, Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Você voltou a si, Tsumugi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.27,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retire imediatamente.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{\i1}Peço desculpas, pai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos quase terminando.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.00,0:11:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aniquile-os!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Coma isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As equipes de Gardes eliminaram a segunda onda.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.05,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimera Tsumugi, recue e recupere o esqueleto Shinatose.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.68,0:11:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Entendido...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.73,0:11:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,O G550 ainda está avançando em direção à Sidonia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.23,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as equipes de Gardes, realinhem-se.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Intercepte o G550.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.99,0:11:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As cores do G550 provavelmente não estão distribuídas uniformemente.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidade, assumam uma formação cêntrica.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.54,0:11:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,O G550 logo entrará em contato com os esquadrões de Gardes.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Formação cêntrica, preparem-se para disparar.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.38,0:12:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Disparo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Várias impactos confirmados.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aproximadamente trezentas Gauna permanecem.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Podemos fazer isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós temos mais do que suficiente munição.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}{\r}Vamos...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, nada de grande agora.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Deslocamento no G550!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A placenta à superfície está mudando de forma.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dê-me uma análise imediatamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:15.07,100 Sights,,0,0,0,,...{\blur0.6}Cem Maravilhas de Sidonia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:12.07,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,...{\blur0.6}Tanques Aquiculturais
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:15.07,100 Sights - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}O Caminho do Vento Livre
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.29,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mantenha o fogo aberto e prepare-se para o que vier.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare com os disparos!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Se afaste dos Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.39,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,É tentando fazer um buraco novamente?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nunca deixarei aquele monstro me engolir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cansado das bocas dos Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}aquele formato...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Há algo dentro dessa cavidade.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Será que...{ur mum's vagina}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.63,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O objeto no fundo da cavidade é considerado uma fusão de todos os Gauna restantes dentro do G550.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Esta estrutura...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Seria um emissor de Partícula Heigus?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um canhão de Partícula Heigus?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.11,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Está alvejando Sidonia diretamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.78,0:14:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A densidade de Partícula Heigus no G550 está aumentando drasticamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quero uma estimativa de danos quando ele disparar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.16,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um impacto superlotaria a armadura da Sidonia e destruiria o navio.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Não...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os Gardes! Ataquem o emissor!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Impedam-no de disparar a qualquer custo!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Não deixe que ele dispare!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dirijam-se rapidamente para o alcance eficaz de fogo!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as janelas, aliste-se no centro daquele buraco!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Apresse-se!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As paredes ao redor estão no caminho.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Temos que nos posicionar acima do buraco.{I want all this sexual imagery out of my head}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Merda!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sidônia!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.04,0:16:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Impacto direto projetado!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.01,0:16:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você parou, Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Feche os olhos, Izana{**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]Tsumugi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx65}{\r}{\i1}O que você—{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.96,0:16:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Falhou.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.63,0:17:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,O feixe foi desviado\Nquando atingiu Tsumugi e Shinatose.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Desviou?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A cibara desviou o ataque?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambos os quadros da Tsumugi e Shinatose\Nainda não foram localizados.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.49,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A densidade de partículas Heigus\Nestá aumentando novamente no interior do G550.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Desta vez, vamos pará-lo!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.66,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Analisando o interior do G550\Natravés da observação de disparo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele vai atirar novamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Todos os quadros, saiam do caminho dos Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.92,0:17:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O G550 alcançará a densidade de disparo de partículas Heigus\Nimediatamente!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.26,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Executando evasão de emergência \Quando o inimigo disparar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Supondo saída e ângulo de tiro iguais.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Recalculando projeção de dano.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze está se distanciando \A alta velocidade.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você está fugindo?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está tentando colidir com ele?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.95,0:18:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Tanikaze[T2]...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.11,0:19:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.78,0:20:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Corpo exposto!{cool original sequence}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.03,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, fogo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.91,0:20:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Disintegração da bolha\NNúcleo do Gauna confirmado.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,G550 foi destruído.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Busque sobreviventes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.99,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Tanikaze?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.31,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, foi um movimento incrivelmente estúpido.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A ameaça inimiga foi derrotada.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.07,0:21:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, procurem os dois mechas\Nque perdermos contato.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.53,0:21:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana, você me ouve?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.20,0:21:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.54,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.85,0:21:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Por favor...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.35,0:21:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajuda-me...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, ajude-me!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.48,0:22:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.69,0:22:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0]...[T1]Tsumugi...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx65}...{\r}Tsumugi é—
