Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.39,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se este mundo está condenado à destruição,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.39,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se esta era é condenada ao caos,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:38.89,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se minha vida estiver em perigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:38.89,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}se meu destino for a morte,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:44.48,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então por que eu devo viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:44.48,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que devo crer para viver?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:50.15,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,1. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Se não tivesse conhecido você,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:50.15,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,2. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}então nunca teria sentido esta dor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:53.57,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,3. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}que me arranca o coração
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:53.57,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,4. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}nunca havia sentido uma dor assim
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:23:00.16,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,5. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}É um requiem grosseiro
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:23:00.16,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,6. {\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}um adeus ao céu distante
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:02.91,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]It is a crude requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:02.91,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,[T0][T1]sora no kanata
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:04.37,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ecoando para
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:04.37,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}narisou foi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:08.21,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}as alturas do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:08.21,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}infindável requeim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.13,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}E até agora
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:10.13,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}ainda assim
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:11.84,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}neste mundo sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:11.84,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}buscando
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:15.26,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu busco
