Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.22,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}por você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.22,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}o que diz respeito a você
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:20.89,Song-ED2-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}Eu me lembro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:20.89,Song-ED2-Rom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}{\blur7.5}até mesmo o prazer de te conhecer
